<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If you have an table with this structure :</p>

<p>CREATE TABLE <code>test</code> (
  <code>id</code> int(11) NOT NULL auto_increment,
  <code>fld1</code> varchar(15) NOT NULL default '',
  <code>fld2</code> varchar(40) NOT NULL default '',
  <code>fld3</code> tinyint(4) NOT NULL default '0',
  PRIMARY KEY  (<code>id</code>),
  UNIQUE KEY <code>LOGIN</code> (<code>fld1</code>,<code>fld3</code>)
)</p>

<p>Zend_DB_Table::Info() =&gt; Primary key = array('fld1', 'fld3');</p>

